```astro
---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import Features from '../components/Features.astro';

const projectInfo = {
  name: "laravel-factory-refactor",
  description: "Refactor the style of factory call from helper to static in Laravel 8.x, 9.x, 10.x.",
  stars: 1,
  forks: 0,
};
---

<Layout>
  <Hero 
    title={projectInfo.name} 
    subtitle={projectInfo.description} 
    stars={projectInfo.stars} 
    forks={projectInfo.forks} 
  />

  <section class="features-section">
    <h2>Features</h2>
    <Features />
  </section>

  <section class="readme-section">
    <h2>README Overview</h2>
    <p>
      This project aims to refactor the style of factory calls in Laravel, transitioning from helper functions to static methods. 
      It supports Laravel versions 8.x, 9.x, and 10.x, providing a more modern and streamlined approach to factory usage.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
```

### 説明
- `Layout`コンポーネントで全体のレイアウトを構成。
- `Hero`コンポーネントでプロジェクト名と説明を表示。
- `Features`コンポーネントで機能を紹介するセクションを追加。
- READMEの一部を表示するセクションを設け、プロジェクトの目的を簡潔に説明。